    <descript>
      <abstract>Data describes soil cores collected at vegetation plots at the Kougarok hill slope located at Kougarok Road, Mile Marker 64 in July 2016. Data upload will be completed January 2017.</abstract>
      <purpose>Soil characteristics measured included soil pH, bulk density, rooting depth, root biomass, depth of the organic horizon, and soil nutrient availability. These variables will characterize the soil environment for vegetation plots at this site.</purpose>
    </descript>
